scripts.dev:kill: powershell.exe -Command "Get-Process -Name node -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Where-Object { (Get-NetTCPConnection -OwningProcess $_.Id -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue).LocalPort -eq 8081 } | Stop-Process -Force; Write-Host 'Metro killed'"
scripts.dev:reload: "%ANDROID_HOME%\platform-tools\adb.exe" shell input text RR || echo 'Make sure emulator is running'
scripts.dev:menu: "%ANDROID_HOME%\platform-tools\adb.exe" shell input keyevent 82 || echo 'Make sure emulator is running'
scripts.dev:clean: cd android && .\gradlew.bat clean && cd .. && npm start -- --reset-cache
